Description: Constitution-driven species distribution modeling pipeline
    for Asian elephants (Elephas maximus) across Bhutan.
    Implements reproducible, governance-compliant SDM workflow with
    multi-model ensemble, CMIP6 climate projections, and uncertainty
    quantification.
